ntime system properties equivalent to `-Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` and `-Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true` to `nativeTest`. Vert.x 5.0.1 manages Netty 4.2.2.Final, whose PlatformDependent0 disables Unsafe by default on Java 24+ unless `sun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` is set. Use an in-process Vert.x HttpServer on localhost for request/response coverage; avoid requiring external services.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The system-property need is tied to JDK 24+/25 and Netty 4.2.x behavior; local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative.\",\n    \"OAuth2WebClient is documented and backed by an optional `io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2` dependency, but base WebClient, sessions, caching, forms, multipart uploads, redirects, and codecs are reachable without adding it.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0979d2ed8502d2ec016a3f4e239bb0819692357bd38f79d2a7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2863, "output": 914, "cacheRead": 31744, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35521, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782533656021, "responseId": "resp_0979d2ed8502d2ec016a3f4e18a1b881968fcca561b944d36f"}, "toolResults": []}
